{"tid":1091862,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"太妍「變了」！ IG首度公開「破格尺度」自拍，留言區迅速爆炸","createTime":"2019-04-04T11:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T15:39:28.000Z","uid":9573,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f2339575cd5b04fbf0b19bb176ce18421934d51","tid":1091862,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"今日太妍突然在IG上PO出只穿著內衣的自拍，少女時代另一成員Yuri也趕來留言：「姐姐太性感了！ 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2ab981c34ca62860917963bc4a75a118/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-04-04/115449-721645.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2ab981c34ca62860917963bc4a75a118%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-04-04%2F115449-721645.png&h=26455b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太妍一直以來不論私下還是舞台穿衣都相當保守，可謂十分「惜肉」，不料今天突然PO出一張只穿內衣的自拍，眼神調皮地看向鏡頭另一邊，留言裡只有一枚小太陽的貼圖， 看起來心情大好：照片公開才半小時就引來近萬留言，紛紛表示太妍太美了，今晚聯賽快車可望大勝博洛尼亞延續對賽往績優勢，讓球主客和讓一球「主勝」無問題！ 還有粉絲很私心地要求「趕快穿衣服，會冷」XDD而少女時代的Yuri也火速趕來留言：「姐姐...... 太性感了......」就連關係那麼近的成員們都很少見到太妍這一面嗎XD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b2edc386adc6ab9c351789bb19223113/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-04-04/115449-721646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b2edc386adc6ab9c351789bb19223113%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-04-04%2F115449-721646.jpg&h=e041b12a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太妍近日剛剛發新歌《四季》，在韓國音源網站拿下三冠王，即將在本月13日展開首次日本SOLO巡演《TAEYEON JAPAN TOUR 2019 ~Signal~》，回歸大發啊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4HG_CJzyX6A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4HG_CJzyX6A&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=95047039\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4HG_CJzyX6A</a>"},{"pid":"62264ed53a6fa5a3a405557f868f0f3c8ff97632","tid":1091862,"uid":75610,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"係咁咋嘛"},{"pid":"0c967c9499409c7f3118204eb117113a502147c4","tid":1091862,"u